2ec514f1-cb64-4fd6-9d71-4a89d8dc5adf.do_description: To make the output, you have to...draw a blue dot one to the right and one up from the original one, follow that pattern until you reach the side, then draw a blue dot one to the left and one up until you reach the other side, repeat until you reach the top
2ec514f1-cb64-4fd6-9d71-4a89d8dc5adf.grid_description: The output grid size...is the same as the old one
2ec514f1-cb64-4fd6-9d71-4a89d8dc5adf.see_description: In the input, you should see...a single blue point at the bottom

ce5324d0-c29f-47fa-8ffb-b9653a25452d.do_description: To make the output, you have to...use blue dots like stairs to reach the top
ce5324d0-c29f-47fa-8ffb-b9653a25452d.grid_description: The output grid size...is the same as the old one
ce5324d0-c29f-47fa-8ffb-b9653a25452d.see_description: In the input, you should see...a single blue point at the bottom

dd24d6d5-c189-4e85-9ab8-1f3c007537fd.do_description: To make the output, you have to...add blue squares in a 45 degree angle pattern back and forward until you reach the top.
dd24d6d5-c189-4e85-9ab8-1f3c007537fd.grid_description: The output grid size...stay the same.
dd24d6d5-c189-4e85-9ab8-1f3c007537fd.see_description: In the input, you should see...a single blue block at the bottom with a black background
